ssor in Environment Contamination Assessment and Remediation at UniSA, Adelaide and collaborates with the CRC CARE at University of Newcastle, NSW. He is former CEO of the South Australian EPA (2012-14) and was CEO of SEPA 2003-12. Campbell is a qualified mediator. Campbell also chaired the South Australian State Radiation Protection Committee and was a member and Chair of the Dounreay Particles Advisory Group 2001-11 and is currently an Independent Advisor to Scottish Government on Underground Coal Gasification.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-07-04T09:23:27Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84707f8d-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-12-21T12:01:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Member, CoRWM","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"846dba2f-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Deputy Chair provides advice and deputises for the Chair when necessary.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-07-22T14:27:11Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Chair, CoRWM","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"e2ffee81-76df-4f69-a8c8-1afa35a63605","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-12-21T11:58:23Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Member, CoRWM","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5bdd2b0c-43ee-4f56-a2e1-35e0a6e2a1c2","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-12-21T12:02:14Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Member, CoRWM","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"25be1203-8689-4e28-9ba0-97a10bd0ecc3","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":